### =========================================================
### Workflow API - Delegation (Phase 3)
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN
@sourceTenantId = REPLACE_SOURCE_TENANT_ID
@targetTenantId = REPLACE_TARGET_TENANT_ID
@partnerLinkId = REPLACE_PARTNER_LINK_ID
@delegationId = REPLACE_DELEGATION_ID

### 1) Grant Delegation (SCOPE_DELEGATION_GRANT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/tenants/{{sourceTenantId}}/delegations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "partnerLinkId": "{{partnerLinkId}}",
  "targetTenantId": "{{targetTenantId}}",
  "resourceType": "PASSPORT",
  "resourceId": "passport_123",
  "permissionCode": "BRAND_RELEASE",
  "expiresAt": null,
  "note": "brand release delegation"
}

### 2) Batch Grant Passport Delegations (SCOPE_DELEGATION_GRANT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/tenants/{{sourceTenantId}}/partners/{{partnerLinkId}}/passport-delegations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "passportIds": ["passport_001", "passport_002", "passport_003"],
  "expiresAt": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "note": "Q2 소매 위임"
}

### 3) Batch Grant - without expiry
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/tenants/{{sourceTenantId}}/partners/{{partnerLinkId}}/passport-delegations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "passportIds": ["passport_001"],
  "expiresAt": null,
  "note": null
}

### 4) List Delegations (SCOPE_DELEGATION_READ)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/tenants/{{sourceTenantId}}/delegations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5) Revoke Delegation (SCOPE_DELEGATION_REVOKE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/delegations/{{delegationId}}/revoke
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "manual revoke"
}

### 6) Internal evaluate (used by product/ledger in future phase)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/internal/delegations/evaluate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "sourceTenantId": "{{sourceTenantId}}",
  "targetTenantId": "{{targetTenantId}}",
  "resourceType": "PASSPORT",
  "resourceId": "passport_123",
  "permissionCode": "BRAND_RELEASE"
}
